Wiring
1. Flame Sensor (KY-026 or similar)
VCC → 5V
GND → GND
D0 (digital output) → Arduino D2

2. Gas Sensor (MQ-2 Module)
VCC → 5V
GND → GND
A0 (analog output) → Arduino A0

3. Relay Module and Buzzer
VCC → 5V
GND → GND
IN → Arduino D4
COM → 5V
NO → Positive side of button
Negative (buzzer) -> GND

4. IR Receiver (HS0038 or similar)
VCC → 5V
GND → GND
OUT → Arduino D3
